                <h2>Goals</h2>
                <p><strong>1. Networking:</strong> To provide a platform where alumni can network with each other, share experiences, and collaborate on professional and personal projects.</p>
                <p><strong>2. Mentorship:</strong> To offer mentorship opportunities for current students by connecting them with experienced alumni who can provide guidance and support.</p>
                <p><strong>3. Event Management:</strong> To organize reunions, webinars, and other events that bring together alumni, students, and faculty for knowledge exchange and socializing.</p>
                <p><strong>4. Fundraising:</strong> To support the institution through fundraising activities that contribute to scholarships, infrastructure, and other development projects.</p>
                <p><strong>5. Career Development:</strong> To assist alumni in their career growth by providing job postings, career advice, and professional development resources.</p>
